{"tid":1075914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★香港福地】公屋單位兒子伴母屍一周　兩人疑餓死！「屋企麵又冇，米又冇....","createTime":"2019-03-24T13:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T07:01:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":148,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"5232a979e72eea5d847eda8d42a23cd901722558","tid":1075914,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/825020/org/93d9a0f713ec914885856ac1a5f386e8.jpg/MGaFjslJywAsGuciGWqatyvLLeNPXL2b0Th9L9E4fS8?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F825020%2Forg%2F93d9a0f713ec914885856ac1a5f386e8.jpg%2FMGaFjslJywAsGuciGWqatyvLLeNPXL2b0Th9L9E4fS8%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=59c709a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n山景邨母子雙屍案，兩人死因至今不明，消息指驗屍初步顯示母親逝世一周後，15歲兒子才相繼離世。死者前夫、任職跟車工人的梁先生接受記者電話訪問稱，難以相信兒子會餓死，認為他的自理能力正常，「屋企麵又冇，米又冇，冇理由餓死個大先。個仔有鑰匙，我絕唔相信佢唔識開門求救，除非搵唔到鑰匙。」他續稱，母子二人曾申領綜援，他曾勸前妻出外工作擴闊生活圈子，近年他每月支付贍養費，三個月前曾探望母子。對於兩人離世，他傷心稱心情難平復，「呢個係家庭慘劇，每個人都唔想，10個有12個都會唔開心。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/118061/山景雙屍案-子疑伴母屍一周-父難信兩人餓死-佢有鑰匙識開門\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F118061%2F%E5%B1%B1%E6%99%AF%E9%9B%99%E5%B1%8D%E6%A1%88-%E5%AD%90%E7%96%91%E4%BC%B4%E6%AF%8D%E5%B1%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8-%E7%88%B6%E9%9B%A3%E4%BF%A1%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA%E9%A4%93%E6%AD%BB-%E4%BD%A2%E6%9C%89%E9%91%B0%E5%8C%99%E8%AD%98%E9%96%8B%E9%96%80&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=a03d4239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/118061/山景雙屍案-子疑伴母屍一周-父難信兩人餓死-佢有鑰匙識開門</a>"},{"pid":"df088ed978d2eeb3b297464716bf4530f9b9a04e","tid":1075914,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/